entry.title: GraceBarbacias: Crop-and-Ecosystems-Modelling
entry.content: Repository for exercises and projects done under the Crop and Ecosystems Modelling (NALA-029) module of Bonn University. The course deals with basics of systems analysis and dynamic process-based modelling using SIMILE, SIMPLACE, and RStudio.
